unique_models.description: Hardcoded modalities for unique models that don't fit standard scraping patterns

aqa.notes: https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/changelog: A new specially tuned model that is trained to answer questions using text passages for grounding generated answers. https://ai.google.dev/competition/projects/ourtownhall: We use the AQA (Attributed Question Answering) feature of Gemini to extract structured data out of unstructured websites.
